00:08:29.070 --> 00:08:34.400 align:middle line:84%
the two notes of A in
the third eye, and also E

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:39.020 align:middle line:84%
for the Sahasrara, or the
crown chakra, when you actually

00:08:39.020 --> 00:08:40.880 align:middle line:84%
come out with those
quite strongly

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:44.510 align:middle line:84%
in the confines of a cab,
that can clear your sinuses

00:08:44.510 --> 00:08:45.680 align:middle line:90%
and it wakes you up.

00:08:45.680 --> 00:08:51.320 align:middle line:84%
It actually helps balance
both hemispheres of the mind.

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:54.740 align:middle line:84%
And it's one of the
nicest ways to stay awake

00:08:54.740 --> 00:08:57.620 align:middle line:84%
that I know for
long drive, so I'll

00:08:57.620 --> 00:09:01.410 align:middle line:90%
throw that in for good measure.

00:09:01.410 --> 00:09:06.900 align:middle line:84%
>> And there's a few things
just to talk about as well,

00:09:06.900 --> 00:09:12.840 align:middle line:84%
because we start with
the oms at the beginning,

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:16.860 align:middle line:84%
and then with the chakra toning,
we start from the base up

00:09:16.860 --> 00:09:21.360 align:middle line:84%
to the crown, and then go back
down from the crown back down

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:23.040 align:middle line:90%
to the base chakra.

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:26.750 align:middle line:84%
You can vary it
as you would like.

00:09:26.750 --> 00:09:29.280 align:middle line:84%
You can just do from
the base to the crown.

00:09:29.280 --> 00:09:32.400 align:middle line:84%
We do both because we
find that going back down

00:09:32.400 --> 00:09:34.800 align:middle line:90%
is also grounding.

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:38.710 align:middle line:84%
But just experiment with this,
because as I said before,

00:09:38.710 --> 00:09:42.540 align:middle line:84%
there's no hard and fast
rules, and it's very freeing.

00:09:42.540 --> 00:09:45.030 align:middle line:90%
So just give anything a try.

00:09:45.030 --> 00:09:47.730 align:middle line:84%
If you want to try
the sound of ah,

00:09:47.730 --> 00:09:51.525 align:middle line:84%
just straight, just do that
and just keep repeating it

00:09:51.525 --> 00:09:54.720 align:middle line:84%
and resonate with the heart,
so focus your attention

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:56.400 align:middle line:90%
with the heart.

00:09:56.400 --> 00:10:00.600 align:middle line:84%
And any sound you can
use on any chakra,

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:03.720 align:middle line:84%
but they do resonate
with particular ones.

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:08.220 align:middle line:84%
So you can say A, and
that's the third eye.

00:10:08.220 --> 00:10:11.340 align:middle line:84%
So you may find as
you're going up and down

00:10:11.340 --> 00:10:14.520 align:middle line:84%
that when you go through
to particular chakras,

00:10:14.520 --> 00:10:19.590 align:middle line:84%
you'll feel more energized or
more clarity within that area.

00:10:19.590 --> 00:10:23.190 align:middle line:84%
I found today as we were doing
the technique, on the way

00:10:23.190 --> 00:10:27.255 align:middle line:84%
back down, my solar
plexus suddenly cleared

00:10:27.255 --> 00:10:32.460 align:middle line:84%
and I had more clarity, and
I got the note right on.

00:10:32.460 --> 00:10:35.530 align:middle line:84%
And you can really
feel when you do that.

00:10:35.530 --> 00:10:37.980 align:middle line:84%
It just sounds
crystal clear, and you

00:10:37.980 --> 00:10:40.950 align:middle line:84%
know that you're in
harmony with that note.

00:10:40.950 --> 00:10:45.450 align:middle line:84%
And I found that when
that happened for me,

00:10:45.450 --> 00:10:48.220 align:middle line:90%
I felt almost bliss.

00:10:48.220 --> 00:10:51.390 align:middle line:84%
So you become very
attuned to yourself

00:10:51.390 --> 00:10:54.450 align:middle line:84%
as well as you're going
through this technique.

00:10:54.450 --> 00:10:58.080 align:middle line:84%
And as I said before,
just have fun with it

00:10:58.080 --> 00:11:01.260 align:middle line:90%
and enjoy and experiment.

00:11:01.260 --> 00:11:02.370 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, indeed.

00:11:02.370 --> 00:11:03.240 align:middle line:90%
Please enjoy.

00:11:03.240 --> 00:11:06.290 align:middle line:90%
